usercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&rurl=translate.google.com&sl=auto&sp=nmt4&tl=en&u=https://www.dienmayxanh.com/kinh-nghiem-hay/cac-che-do-thuong-thay-tren-may-lanh-795107&xid=17259,15700022,15700186,15700190,15700256,15700259,15700262,15700265,15700271&usg=ALkJrhiITpksH-ncXTxjwIdCjcCTHtYwDg#gio-de-chiu\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Pleasant wind blowing (for children, the elderly)\">Comfortable wind blowing</a> mode</span> </h3><p> <span class=\"notranslate\"> With this mode, the swing fan is designed upwards to help prevent cold air flow directly from you, causing aches and chills.</span> </p><p></p><h3> <span class=\"notranslate\"> <a href=\"https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&rurl=translate.google.com&sl=auto&sp=nmt4&tl=en&u=https://www.dienmayxanh.com/kinh-nghiem-hay/cong-nghe-lam-lanh-khu-mui-tren-may-lanh-daikin-588199&xid=17259,15700022,15700186,15700190,15700256,15700259,15700262,15700265,15700271&usg=ALkJrhinR57Vrs2yIwl8pXwi4MM5SLDAqw#apatit-titan\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Titanium Apatite Photocatalytic Deodorising Filter\">Titanium Apatite Photocatalytic Deodorising</a> Filter filters dust, mold, and deodorant effectively</span> </h3><p> <span class=\"notranslate\"> Equipped with Titanium Apatite photocatalytic <a href=\"https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&rurl=translate.google.com&sl=auto&sp=nmt4&tl=en&u=https://www.dienmayxanh.com/may-lanh&xid=17259,15700022,15700186,15700190,15700256,15700259,15700262,15700265,15700271&usg=ALkJrhhg3gjk3qomcbhWglagKUerebv4Bg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"air-conditioner\">air-</a> purifying filter, the <a href=\"https://translate.googleusercontent.com/translate_c?depth=1&rurl=translate.google.com&sl=auto&sp=nmt4&tl=en&u=https://www.dienmayxanh.com/may-lanh&xid=17259,15700022,15700186,15700190,15700256,15700259,15700262,15700265,15700271&usg=ALkJrhhg3gjk3qomcbhWglagKUerebv4Bg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"air-conditioner\">air conditioner</a> will filter out bacteria, dirt a